name: Kung-Fucat
description: While the majority of Meme Coins have zero utility, $KFUCAT will act as the utility token of the upcoming Kung-FuCat game. Kung-FuCat will offer Play To Earn opportunities. Players can earn $KFUCAT in-game and rare items by winning battles, participating in special events, and completing challenging quests. These items can be traded or sold.
